                function UpdateMaintenanceCountdownTimer() {
                    var minutesTillDowntime = Math.round((maintenanceStartTime - serverTime) / 60000);

                    if (minutesTillDowntime &lt;= 1) {
                        document.getElementById(htmlElementID).innerHTML = 'less than 1 minute';
                    }
                    else {
                        document.getElementById(htmlElementID).innerHTML = minutesTillDowntime + ' minutes';
                        setTimeout(function () {

                            UpdateMaintenanceCountdownTimer();
                        }, 1000);
                    }
